{
  "stem": "16245.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that meant that they had the rabbis who were dressed like ministers of religion, much the same as in Australia, for instance, Rabbi Danglow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the sermon was preached in Hungarian, which in those days, was quite-- quite progressive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was the only one I ever went to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not an awful lot, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that we were different, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but there was really no persecution.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You may get a beating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You might even [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] get remarks passed on you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance, on the Day of Atonement, the Jewish kids were the butt of every joke in town, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As you were walking to the synagogue or some place-- are you-- are you starving?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's probably the worst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do remember though Easter processions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a time when it really wasn't advisable for Jewish kids to be around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two churches in town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the procession went from one to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it wasn't really tactful for a Jew to be around, put it that way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1936.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They moved to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was really the lifesaver.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they would have stayed in Nagykanisza, none of us would be here today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Basically business reasons.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father thought he'd do better in-- in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1936.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a lot, but nevertheless, you couldn't shut yourself away from it, even a kid who was-- who knew nothing about politics.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a six, seven, eight-year-old kid knows nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nevertheless, the Berlin Olympic Games, for instance, brought it home.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
